Package: org.lappsgrid.jupyter.groovy.handler

[Groovy] Class CompleteHandler

      • org.lappsgrid.jupyter.groovy.handler.CompleteHandler

      • The code completion handler. The CompleteHandler is called by Jupyter to determine if the line of code just entered should be executed immediately or if more input is required. It also compiles the code to ensure that it is valid.

        Authors:
        Keith Suderman
